    "The SUCCEED system allows for the registration and browsing of upcycling cases.",
    "By referencing past cases, it is expected that one can learn how to utilize materials and efficiently advance developments with similar backgrounds or technical proximity.",
    "The system features a search function, enabling the search for cases using keywords.",
    "A challenge with the SUCCEED system is that if users do not have a preconceived idea of the service they wish to develop, browsing upcycling cases alone may not clearly demonstrate how each case can be useful for specific service development.",
    "ChallengeA challenge in facilitating a development-oriented approach tailored to individual needs is the high cost of developing finely personalized services."
